Ranger Tracking Placeable

- Place this placeable anywhere in an area to enable ranger tracking in that area.

- Set the Will Save of the placed tracker to the DC to successfully track in the area.

Tracking roll is made as d20 + ranger level against the DC modified by the distance from the critter.
